1.2 Officials of the Government of the Republic of Uzbekistan attended in networking with non-Art 5 and other Art 5 countries. At least 9 (including 2 women) high-level officials from Uzbekistan have participated in International Conferences and Workshops related to the International cooperation on Montreal Protocol, including in the 5th Meeting of the GEF Assembly; and well represented in other related meetings and workshops;
2.2. A list of key legal and regulatory documentation related to phasing-out of HCFCs as well as options on control exercised by the customs authorities destruction of ODS identified. Review for possible gaps identification to be conducted further;
